	"system":{
		"description":{
			"value":"<p class=\"flavour\"><i>This brass wand, which resembles a miniaturized horn, will drive your enemies back with a wave of thunder, or drop them with a shock wave.</i></p><p class=\"basics\"><b>Implement</b><b>:</b> Wand</p>\n<p class=\"basics\"><b>Enhancement Bonus:</b> Attack Rolls and Damage Rolls</p><p class=\"basics\"><b>Critical:</b> +3d8 thunder critical damage</p>\n<p class=\"subheading\"><b>Property:</b></p> <p>Once during each of your turns, when you hit with a thunder attack using this wand, you can push one creature adjacent to you 1 square.</p>\n<p class=\"subheading\"><b>Power ✦ Encounter (Standard Action)</b></p><p><i>Attack:</i> Close blast 5 (creatures and objects in the blast); the wand's level + 3 vs. Fortitude.</p><p><i>Hit:</i> You push the target up to a number of squares equal to the wand's enhancement bonus and knock it prone.</p><p class=\"subheading\"><b>Power ✦ Daily (No Action)</b></p><p><i>Trigger:</i> You hit a target with a thunder attack using this wand.</p><p><i>Effect:</i> Each creature adjacent to the target takes 10 thunder damage and falls prone.</p><p>Level 23 or 28: 20 thunder damage.</p>",
